@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        .about-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

            .about-section h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #343a40;
            }

            .about-section p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                color: #495057;
            }

            .about-section .highlight {
                background-color: #fff3cd;
                border-left: 5px solid #ffeeba;
                padding: 15px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .about-section .contact {
                margin-top: 30px;
                padding: 20px;
                background-color: #e9ecef;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }

                .about-section .contact h3 {
                    font-size: 1.5rem;
                    color: #343a40;
                }

                .about-section .contact p {
                    font-size: 1rem;
                    color: #6c757d;
                }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container about-section">
        <h1 class="text-center">Our Story</h1>

        <p>Welcome to <strong>Serenity Sanctuary</strong>, where we believe that candles are more than just a source of light—they are an essential element of creating a peaceful and inviting atmosphere in your home. Our journey began with a passion for crafting exquisite candles that not only illuminate but also inspire and soothe.</p>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Our Mission:</strong> Our mission is to bring serenity and warmth to your life through meticulously designed candles. Each candle is crafted with love, using premium, eco-friendly ingredients to ensure a clean and long-lasting burn. Our collection features a range of enchanting scents and beautifully designed products that cater to your unique tastes and preferences.</p>
        </div>

        <p>We invite you to explore our collection and experience the serenity that our candles bring. Thank you for choosing <strong>Serenity Sanctuary</strong> to be a part of your daily moments of peace and joy.</p>

        <div class="contact">
            <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
            <p>Feel free to reach out to us with any questions or feedback—we are always happy to hear from our valued customers.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
